#text=My friend and I were running late this morning .
#text=We needed to catch our plane , there was no time to shower we just had to grab our luggage and run .
#text=Since we were not flying out of the country we did n't need our passports , but we made sure to grab our boarding passes before we left the house .
#text=We called a cab and headed to the airport .
#text=After we arrived at the airport , we checked our bags and went through security .
#text=After going through security we headed to our gate and waited to board .
#text=When they finally said they were boarding our section we boarded the aircraft and put our checked luggage in the overhead compartments and took our seats .
#text=Our part was done , we now just had to wait for the plane to take off .
#text=I was chewing gum so that my ears would not pop when we took off .
